title: Peter Kaack
text: Peter Kaack (born 9 December 1943) is a retired <a href="Germany">German</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He spent ten seasons in the <a href="Fu%C3%9Fball-Bundesliga">Bundesliga</a> with <a href="Eintracht%20Braunschweig">Eintracht Braunschweig</a>.
